    "summary": "Sourcegraph exposes a GraphQL debug API, a streaming search HTTP API, a newer external HTTP API at `/api-reference`, an MCP server, an analytics HTTP API on analytics.sourcegraph.com, and the `src` CLI; all documented surfaces require authentication.",
    "description": "Sourcegraph provides code search, code navigation, repository analysis, and related developer tooling for source code across many repositories. It is offered as Sourcegraph Cloud and self-hosted deployments, with separate analytics features for usage and performance data.",
